Some consider it to be definitively his greatest story. Others say it made him a scapegoat for all the problems facing the publication. There are those who call its animated adaption the greatest DC Animated movie of all time, while a vocal few voiced anger by the changes that were to come of it. We're talking about Flashpoint and can you believe it's been 10 years since the groundbreaking time travel epic hit comic stands? Now, a full decade later join us as we recap the comic, talk about its adaptations, and debate the merits of the New 52 in this latest edition of the Major Issues Podcast.

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.